--start mongod with WireTiger StorageEngine
killall mongod
mkdir WT
mongod -dbpath WT -storageEngine wireTiger

StoreEngine
get data from persistent storage to virtual memory
manage, allocate memory

MMAPv1(DEFAULT)
-based on mmap system call
-Collection Level Concurency
-allow inplace update
-power of two size, 3->4,7->8,19->32



Wired Tiger
-Document Level Concurrency
-Compression functionality - data and indexes
-No in place update


